VendorCode: The Vendor Code field is an alphanumeric field and should exactly match how it is setup in the system.  If an exact match is not found, the row will be marked as invalid and skipped in the upload.
GLCodes: The GL Code field is an alphanumeric field and should exactly match how it is setup in the system.  If an exact match is not found, the row will be marked as invalid and skipped in the upload.
Integration Package: This is a required field.  This field is a text field and will be compared for an exact match in the system.  If no exact match is found, the row will be marked invalid.  To find the integration package name, refer to the Integration Package field on any Active Property in Property Setup.
